reviews.review_text: FOB and charlie this is a THE Aud. for this date.  by far and away a huge upgrade over the one with 575,000+ downloads.  thanks again Mr. Miller!!

I was sent here by jbsbmt ....who stated that he appreciates a good aud tape. This ia a great, Great, GREAT aud tape of a killer show. 5 stars for both preformance and recording.

Now then, jbsbmt,and all you other fans of good aud tape of a good show, lemmie steer you to 1985/11/10 Bredan Byrne...this is the copy I like the most:

http://archive.org/details/gd1985-11-10.nak-beyer.suraci.79689.sbeok.flac16

Enjyy.
- Nice treatment of a brilliant show. On this occasion, the band are all the more incredible for being tight and businesslike. Not a lot of time spent on Drums & Space, just intense playing.
